data.description: Beautifully updated Ranch home with Great location in Yukon, This wonderful 4-bed 2-bath would make the perfect first-time home or investment property in Yukon. As you enter the home you will fall in love with the tall ceilings, natural light, upgraded flooring throughout the living room and kitchen areas, and spacious open floorplan. The kitchen was meticulously designed with an open floor plan featuring an island with barstool seating, granite countertops, walk-in pantry and stainless steel appliances. The oversized master suite comes with an ensuite equipped with double vanity, large shower, and a spacious walk-in closet. The property is fully fenced and is perfect for your family's pets.
